THIRD-PARTY DATA
----------------
This platform builds on third-party datasets (ECMWF SEAS5, Meteo-France
System 9, ERA5, CHIRPS, CESM2, COBE-SST 2, GPCP, Berkeley Earth, Natural
Earth, and others). Each dataset remains under its own license and citation
requirements - see the Methodology page for full sources and DOIs:
  https://iadicarlo.github.io/ensoscope/methodology.html#data-sources

The CC BY 4.0 license above applies to original ENSOscope content, not to the
underlying third-party data, which you must attribute separately.
